high_descs: Turn right and walk to the black stand in front of you
Pick up the empty toilet paper roll that is sitting on the black stand
Turn around and take a few steps then hang right and walk to the toilet paper holder that is hanging on the wall by the toilet
Place the empty toilet paper roll on the toilet paper holder
anns.task_desc: Place an empty toilet paper roll on a toilet paper holder.

high_descs: Turn right and walk to the small dark table
Pick up the toilet paper roll from the table
Turn around to the right and walk up to the toiler paper holder on the wall
Put the toilet paper roll on the toilet paper holder
anns.task_desc: Put the toilet paper roll on the toilet paper holder

high_descs: Turn right and walk to the black table.
Pick up the toilet paper roll on the far side of the table.
Turn around and walk toward the sink, then turn left to face the toilet paper dispenser.
Place the toilet paper roll on the dispenser.
anns.task_desc: Put the toilet paper roll on the toilet paper dispenser.

high_descs: Turn right, head to the black table by the door
Take the empty toilet paper roll from the table
Turn around, head to the toilet
Put the toilet paper paper roll on the holder

high_descs: Turn to the right and find the black table.
Pick up the empty toilet paper roll from the table.
Take the roll and turn around, then turn right to face the wall.
Place the toilet paper roll on the holder, beside the toilet.

high_descs: Move to the black side table on top of the red rug
Pick up the brown tube on top of the table
Carry the tube to the toilet paper holder on the wall to the right of the toilet
